	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simulatque me D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1553">Hochholtzero</persName> adeoque D. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallero</persName> commendaveras, nolo te lateat scholę <placeName type="auto_name">Aroviensi</placeName> paulo ante meum <persName type="auto_name">[Lienhard</persName> <persName type="auto_name">Meyer?</persName>] adventum pręfectum quendam <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensem</placeName> iuvenem.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque ego <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName> profectus a fratribus magistratui commendatus sum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magistratus porro ad primam occasionem se mihi prospecturum pollicitus est; D. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName> autem literas vocationis meę ad te missurum recepit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde rogo te, domine mi, ut reliquis tuis in me beneficiis hoc addas: si pervenerint ad te literę, mihi quamprimum vel <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l50" cert="high">Episcopicellam</placeName> vel <placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiam</placeName> ad fratrem meum <persName type="auto_name">Lütfrid Jung</persName> vocatum perferri cures.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus et te et ecclesiam vestram una cum familia tua in sua pace conservet.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc paucis ad te in presens ex itinere; alias fusius scribendi dabitur (spero) oportunitas.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2512" cert="high">Badenę</placeName> 3a iulii 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1754">Iohannes Iung</persName> nunc Episcopalicellę.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeclaro <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię antistiti D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, domino suo observandissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
